Package: geozarr
Title: GeoZarr Conventions for Geospatial Data in Zarr Stores
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Patrick", "Van Laake", , "patrick@vanlaake.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: GeoZarr is being defined in terms of a number of community 
    conventions built on top of the Zarr specification. These conventions
    specify how Zarr metadata is to be interpreted to attach semantic meaning to
    the data in the Zarr array providing the metadata. This package implements a
    number of community conventions enabling the R community to use geospatial
    data stored in Zarr.
